column5: Heading to Lac Suel on the 16th. Are there any decent leeches between Fort Frances and Sioux Lookout? Thanks for the help.

Yes, there is an excellent place in Ft Francis that opens at 6am right at Rainy River Dock. They sell everything you need. There is also a bait shop in Dryden which we have used before and they work out well. Do not wait until you get to SL.
